{"tid":1029260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓政府禁國民上Pornhub","createTime":"2019-02-20T06:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T09:36:34.000Z","uid":228995,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac7a53625313fc85c8b1ce405f3227a4ac5bc9d","tid":1029260,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"泡菜 = 中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n//<br />\n南韓政府禁止國民瀏覽近900個色情和賭博網頁，包括全球最大色情網站「Pornhub」，惹來爭議。有專家認為南韓的舉動似足「中國式網絡審查」，不少人認為當局要在保護女性免受「色情報復」（revenge porn）和網絡自由之間取得平衡。<br />\n<br />\n南韓放送通訊審議委員會（KCSC）本月11日起，以伺服器名稱指示（Server Name Indication，簡稱SNI）方式，阻擋國民連上895個含「有害」內容的海外網站。有關方式是當有網民以https瀏覽色情和賭博網站時，政府可打開用戶的數據包（data packet）找出他們欲到訪的網站並作出封阻。<br />\n<br />\n有關方式引來不少爭議，有近25萬人在青瓦台的網站聯署抗議，有人寫道：「很遺憾南韓看來正追隨中國步伐去審查互聯網」；周六亦有約100人在首爾車站廣場抗議。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n會唔會最後引發革命？<br />\n香港有雨傘革命<br />\n泡菜有pornhub革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f0b28fd1a46f7a6e78ca30ed736e8604c80b90","tid":1029260,"uid":192581,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"AV光碟市場要復興了"},{"pid":"b84cd8e353d28e3288f2300cdabc1344030c5b6a","tid":1029260,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"韓狗出名性變態 唔比佢地上就岩"},{"pid":"665a1493b1e6c43f0dffd827cc6189b245b67d27","tid":1029260,"uid":6535,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:23:59.000Z","msg":"睇Kpop MV打J咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0182f20aa25af56666708b1db578d6ba1c0e40","tid":1029260,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:23:59.000Z","msg